Package model

This is a package for all classes which are responsible for storing data.

    Digram
    This is a class for a replacement digram which is called Digram.
    DigramList
    This class represents the DigramList for basic digrams.
    Edge
    This class is an abstract class for the simple edges and hyper edges.
    EquivalenceclassMapper
    This class is a helper class for the mapping function of a digram.
